race.description: Book For Christmas Meeting Sat 6th Dec Hcp
race.comment: DALT JAZ (6) is ready to win after he just missed last time, beaten a neck into third over 1100m at this track after being prominent from the outset. Drawn to go forward and is nicely placed to feature in the finish. ZAYA (10) was just out of the money two runs back then again just missed the frame last start over 1100m here, beaten 0.7 lengths into fourth. Expect a better run this time. ANSWERING (4) showed good early speed and raced on the pace last start before fading to finish fifth, beaten 1.4 lengths, over 1100m at this venue. Top-three conveyance. SINGULAR (1) turned things around last start and got the job done by a neck over 1100m at this course. Anticipating another big run.
